<section id="consent-overview">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
    </span>
    Consent Overview
  </h2>

  <p class="lead">When you provide your phone number and opt in, you agree to receive text messages from Ferni to support your coaching journey.</p>

  <div class="callout callout--highlight">
    <strong>Key Points</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>SMS consent is <strong>optional</strong>—not required to use Ferni</li>
      <li>You can <strong>opt out anytime</strong> by texting STOP</li>
      <li><strong>Message and data rates</strong> may apply</li>
      <li>We will <strong>never sell</strong> your phone number</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3>What This Document Covers</h3>
  <p>This SMS Terms & Consent document explains:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>What types of messages you'll receive</li>
    <li>How often we'll text you</li>
    <li>Costs you may incur</li>
    <li>How to opt out or modify your preferences</li>
    <li>Your rights under the Telephone Consumer Protection Act (TCPA)</li>
    <li>How we protect your phone number</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Agreement</h3>
  <p>By providing your mobile phone number and opting in to SMS communications:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>You consent to receive autodialed, recurring text messages from Ferni AI, Inc.</li>
    <li>You confirm you are the account holder or authorized user of the phone number</li>
    <li>You agree to these SMS Terms & Consent</li>
    <li>You acknowledge that consent is not a condition of purchase</li>
  </ul>
</section>

