      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
    </span>
    Message Types & Content
  </h2>

  <p>Here's what you can expect to receive from Ferni via SMS:</p>

  <h3>Coaching Reminders</h3>
  <div class="callout">
    <p><em>"Hey! Ready for your check-in with Maya? She's been thinking about your morning routine progress."</em></p>
  </div>
  <p>Gentle nudges to reconnect with your coaching sessions. These help you stay on track with your personal development goals.</p>

  <h3>Personalized Check-Ins</h3>
  <div class="callout">
    <p><em>"How did that conversation with your manager go yesterday? We're here if you want to talk through it."</em></p>
  </div>
  <p>Follow-ups on topics from your recent sessions. Our team remembers what matters to you and checks in at meaningful moments.</p>

  <h3>Habit Tracking Nudges</h3>
  <div class="callout">
    <p><em>"Day 7 of your meditation streak! That's a full week. How's it feeling?"</em></p>
  </div>
  <p>Encouragement for the habits you're building. Celebrate milestones and get gentle reminders to keep going.</p>

  <h3>Account Notifications</h3>
  <div class="callout">
    <p><em>"Your Ferni subscription renews in 3 days. Questions? Reply or call us."</em></p>
  </div>
  <p>Important updates about your account, billing, and service changes. These are informational, not promotional.</p>

  <h3>Verification & Security</h3>
  <div class="callout">
    <p><em>"Your Ferni verification code is 482953. This expires in 10 minutes."</em></p>
  </div>
  <p>One-time codes for account verification and security. These may be sent even if you've opted out of other messages.</p>

  <h3>Message Personalization</h3>
  <p>Messages are personalized based on:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your conversation history and goals</li>
    <li>The AI coaching persona you're working with</li>
    <li>Your time zone and preferences</li>
    <li>Your recent activity and progress</li>
  </ul>
</section>

