<section id="opt-out">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
    </span>
    How to Opt Out
  </h2>

  <div class="callout callout--important">
    <strong>Text STOP to cancel anytime.</strong>
    <p>Reply STOP to any Ferni message to immediately unsubscribe from all SMS communications. You'll receive a confirmation message, and we won't text you again unless you opt back in.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>SMS Keywords</h3>
  <div class="data-table">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Keyword</th>
          <th>What It Does</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>STOP</strong></td>
          <td>Unsubscribe from all Ferni text messages</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>STOP ALL</strong></td>
          <td>Same as STOP—unsubscribe from all messages</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>QUIT</strong></td>
          <td>Same as STOP—unsubscribe from all messages</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>CANCEL</strong></td>
          <td>Same as STOP—unsubscribe from all messages</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>UNSUBSCRIBE</strong></td>
          <td>Same as STOP—unsubscribe from all messages</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>HELP</strong></td>
          <td>Get support information and contact details</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>INFO</strong></td>
          <td>Same as HELP—get program information</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h3>Other Ways to Opt Out</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>In-App:</strong> Settings → Notifications → Disable SMS</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> Send "Opt out of SMS" to <a href="mailto:support@ferni.ai">support@ferni.ai</a></li>
    <li><strong>Phone:</strong> Call <a href="tel:+14844813081">1 (484) 481-3081</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h3>What Happens After Opting Out</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>You'll receive a confirmation: "You've been unsubscribed from Ferni SMS. Reply START to re-subscribe."</li>
    <li>All coaching, reminder, and notification messages will stop</li>
    <li>You may still receive transactional messages (verification codes) if you initiate them</li>
    <li>Your Ferni account remains active—only SMS is disabled</li>
    <li>Your phone number remains on file (for account association) until you request deletion</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Processing Time</h3>
  <p>Opt-out requests are processed immediately. In rare cases, you may receive one additional message that was already in our sending queue before your request was processed.</p>
</section>

