<section id="tcpa-rights">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
    </span>
    Your TCPA Rights
  </h2>

  <p>The Telephone Consumer Protection Act (TCPA) gives you important rights regarding text messages. Here's what you should know:</p>

  <h3>Your Rights Under TCPA</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prior express consent required:</strong> We cannot send you automated text messages without your consent</li>
    <li><strong>Right to revoke:</strong> You can revoke consent at any time by any reasonable means (texting STOP, calling us, emailing us)</li>
    <li><strong>No consent required for purchase:</strong> We cannot require SMS consent as a condition of purchasing our services</li>
    <li><strong>Clear disclosure:</strong> We must clearly disclose the nature of messages before you opt in</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Our Compliance</h3>
  <p>Ferni is committed to TCPA compliance. We:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Only send messages to numbers that have opted in</li>
    <li>Honor all opt-out requests promptly</li>
    <li>Maintain records of consent</li>
    <li>Include opt-out instructions in messages</li>
    <li>Identify ourselves in all messages</li>
    <li>Respect the National Do-Not-Call Registry</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Exemptions</h3>
  <p>Certain messages may be sent even after you opt out:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>One-time password (OTP) verification codes you've requested</li>
    <li>Responses to messages you initiate</li>
    <li>Important security alerts about your account</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Filing Complaints</h3>
  <p>If you believe your TCPA rights have been violated, you may:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@ferni.ai">legal@ferni.ai</a></li>
    <li>File a complaint with the FCC at <a href="https://consumercomplaints.fcc.gov">consumercomplaints.fcc.gov</a></li>
    <li>File a complaint with the FTC at <a href="https://reportfraud.ftc.gov">reportfraud.ftc.gov</a></li>
  </ul>
</section>

