  <h3>Messages Arriving Late</h3>
  <p>SMS messages may be delayed due to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Carrier network congestion</li>
    <li>Poor signal at time of sending</li>
    <li>Phone being off or in airplane mode</li>
    <li>Carrier maintenance windows</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>STOP/HELP Not Working</h3>
  <p>If SMS keywords aren't working:</p>
  <ul>
